Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互道初次見面的時候總會有種心跳的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人與人的相遇是美妙的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們要把這個瞬間當作寶物來對待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窗戶 什麼時候打開的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著各種各樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺到新的一天開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託妳了 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 這裡是亞利亞公司 多謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 多謝來電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得本人想要聽艾莉西亞的語音留言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而特地打電話來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要妨礙我？鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是什麼鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要妳還留著那個長鬢的話就一直都是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了那不是鬢角了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您想預約鳳尾舟的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爺很忙 沒空和鬢子談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:55.55,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那份 美妙的奇蹟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡 新威尼斯的春天就快結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我第一天到AQUA的日子算起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉眼已經快20個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以AQUA的年曆來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有4個月左右就滿整整一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二個夏天也就快來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鳥離開巢穴時 也是這種心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城市就是新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說是和我想像中的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是超乎我的想像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個城市 我一定會讓你們看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將成為一個出色的領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 多謝來電 這裡是亞利亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我想坐艾莉西亞小姐的鳳尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何我都想坐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預約都滿了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？那麼其他人也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這裡只有我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因為還是半熟手 一個人不能接待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是個出色的領航員的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果不是艾莉西亞前輩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許客人也無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們去練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是去練習吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是半熟手 不能接待…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始我們就是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要喊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綁架啊 來人啊 救命啊 就這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這是我想出來的不讓船搖晃的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是晃得很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡坐鳳尾舟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不太喜歡 而且又慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個孩子是剛才打電話來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 妳是從地球來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前也是住在地球上的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳一個人來的？這是不可能的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸媽媽一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和地球比起來是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有汽車 出門幾乎都是用走路的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜也是自己去買材料回來自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟按慣例也是自己來划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是累人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很喜歡像這樣全部都要自己來做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上是做不到的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告訴我妳的名字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫水無燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要坐我的鳳尾舟？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在審問我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和聽說的不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子不是遊客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的朋友 叫小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從地球來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就是白坐船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 如妳所說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快點下船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們兩個誰划得好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳問誰划得好的話 當然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 請妳來划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 做朋友又沒什麼關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 好不容易相識一場 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 藍華 我們去看艾莉西亞前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 妳真的很喜歡艾莉西亞前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是晃得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為準確的時間和愉快的交談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是姬屋公司的格言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA從被改造到適合人類居住已約有150年了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時至今日 被人稱之為「水之星球」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而新威尼斯則以過去地球上的城市威尼斯為原型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳突然之間說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想有個導遊會比較有趣點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但妳說的一點都沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且對白坐船的也不用服務得如此周到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 好不容易來這一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是想讓她喜歡上新威尼斯再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳喜歡這個城市嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初只是嚮往著要成為帥氣的領航員才來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在卻越來越喜歡AQUA和新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不方便的交通 悠閒的時間 這些全部都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城市 一定是由奇蹟所構成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇蹟？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 在曾經沒有空氣和水的這顆星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建造這座城市的人們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾多回憶和思念聚集而產生出的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美妙的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的相遇也許也是奇蹟之一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賣烤奶油馬鈴薯的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤奶油馬鈴薯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂 在家裡也吃過 並不怎麼喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和在地球上吃起來的感覺完全不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還是嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳有錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢 有錢卻白坐船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我們也不能收她的錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬鈴薯好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上賣的一般是切成小塊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃起來好像很不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？多謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長 我們要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想應該讓熟練的人來划會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的 燈里還有秘密絕招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使出全力吧 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為燈里她在地球作練習時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陰差陽錯地學會了逆划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在逆划的時候她可是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣划沒問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 就這樣筆直過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微左邊點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然採取了意外的舉動 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 藍華也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子叫小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們也做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 再見了 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 妳一直想見艾莉西亞前輩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上打電話來的就是小愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說想要坐艾莉西亞前輩的鳳尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這裡之前 我非常討厭AQUA和新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為之前我姐姐的新婚旅行就是來的這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年齡差得很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 所以她一直把我當小孩子對待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行回來後 就一直對我說AQUA的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然喜歡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我稍微有點討厭她的誇耀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我連AQUA和新威尼斯也討厭起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 妳今天為什麼來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想如果實際來一次的話 也許會喜歡上這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拜託了爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他們剛帶我來到這裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處都非常無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也坐過其它的鳳尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不過如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我想說 還是非得坐姐姐最為誇耀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞的鳳尾舟才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻坐不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是妳就決定坐燈里的鳳尾舟對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天能坐上妳們的船真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤奶油馬鈴薯非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆划也非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去後我也要向姐姐誇耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 妳姐姐並不是在誇耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許她是想告訴小愛AQUA上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 妳想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不是也想告訴別人妳所喜歡的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是對於妳喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就想告訴姐姐今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為什麼 忽然想聽姐姐的閒談了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了燈里妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來也許有一天 我也會喜歡上這座城市的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從討厭轉變成喜歡 也許是奇蹟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是給各位添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道該怎麼道歉才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 真的今天就要離開這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想在明天的午休時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去拜託艾莉西亞前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們下次再來這裡的話 我一定會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會發郵件給妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次來的時候 我還想坐燈里妳的鳳尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 妳要盡快成為出色的領航員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 還有這個 請交給艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩位我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在鳳尾舟上開始吵架的新婚夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旅行中 第一次瞭解到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此所不瞭解的討厭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知所措呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來和好如初了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 雖然那時候真的很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好幸福的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從討厭轉變成喜歡 雖然需要點努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能做到這點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳所喜歡的人就會成為妳所珍惜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳所珍惜的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份奇蹟 能夠靠努力來獲取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛的奇蹟也許是靠她自己得來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 想變得更喜歡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是小愛所帶來的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 今天也是美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 燈里妳的哪一天不是美好的一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.13,0:24:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 特別的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們一起度過美好的時光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
